    public interface AHOrgModel
extends com.liferay.portal.model.BaseModel<AHOrg>
    The base model interface for the AHOrg service. Represents a row in the "AHORG" database table, with each column mapped to a property of this class.

    This interface and its corresponding implementation AHOrgModelImpl exist only as a container for the default property accessors generated by ServiceBuilder. Helper methods and all application logic should be put in AHOrgImpl.
